snippet.description:
ISHQ MAI KHAIRAAT NAHI HOTI
When fate ties three lives together, love lights the way, but struggles darken the path, and sacrifice becomes their only choice. 7th Sky Entertainment proudly presents the highly anticipated mega drama serial Sanwal Yaar Piya, starring the blockbuster trio Feroze Khan, Durefishan Saleem, and Ahmed Ali Akbar.

#SanwalYaarPiya is coming soon only on Drama Bazar

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Danish Nawaz
Writer: Hashim Nadeem Khan

Cast: Feroze Khan, Durefishan Saleem, Ahmed Ali Akbar, Yasir Nawaz, Zainab Qayoom, Deepak Perwani, Ali Tahir, Erum Akhtar, Sidra Niazi, Nayyer Ejaz, Saqib Sumeer, Kamran Jeelani, Rashid Farooqi.

snippet.title: TROPHIES ARE GONE?!
snippet.description:
Learn everything about the biggest matchmaking change in Clash of Clans history and what it means for you.
This change is coming with our next big update, but we wanted to give you a heads up so you can prepare.
For the first time ever, you will be able to choose how you want to Clash. Whether you're looking for competitive battles or a more relaxed way to play, this change gives you the freedom to pick the experience that fits your goals.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

#clashofclans

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Lyrical Video | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the lyrical video of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

snippet.title: Shinchan Meets Mahabali! 🎉 Franklin Gets a Superbike Gift | GTA 5 Malayalam Onam Special 🚀😂
snippet.description:
✨ GTA 5 Malayalam Onam Special 2025 – Franklin, Shinchan & Mahabali Storyline!
In this epic Onam episode, Shiranui surprises Franklin with a superbike gift 🚴🔥. Franklin is super happy, but Shinchan crashes the bike in his funny style 😂. Feeling sad after Franklin scolds him, Shinchan runs away in the rain 🌧️… where he meets none other than Mahabali – the King of Kerala! 👑🌴

Mahabali shows his powers, fixes Franklin’s bike, and even spawns Kinder Joy 🍫. Together they go for Onam shopping at Trevor’s fruit & vegetable shop 🥭🍌. But when the taxi villains try to attack, Mahabali uses his magic to send them flying 🚖💥. Finally, Shinchan shows a Lamborghini, and Mahabali spawns supercars for everyone 🏎️✨.

👉 Stay tuned for Part 2 – the Onam celebration with full fun, sadya, pookalam, and more! 🌸🍲

🎥 Don’t forget to LIKE 👍, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more GTA 5 Malayalam funny videos with Franklin, Shinchan, and family!

Przekształciłem oryginalne dzieło, dodając własną, unikalną wartość, taką jak wysokiej jakości montaż i efekty specjalne, aby stworzyć zupełnie nowe, oryginalne zwiastuny filmowe. Są to utwory zależne w rozumieniu amerykańskiej ustawy o prawie autorskim 17 U.S.C. § 101 i jako takie mogą być chronione przed roszczeniami z tytułu praw autorskich na podstawie zasady dozwolonego użytku.

snippet.description:
Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. snippet.title: गणपति विसर्जन स्पेशल 2025 🙏 निरोप घेतो देवा आता आज्ञा असावी Nirop Gheto Deva 🙏 Ganpati Visarjan Geet
snippet.description:
🙏 "गणपती बाप्पा मोरया... पुन्हा वर्षी लवकर या!"
हा निरोपाचा क्षण आहे भावपूर्ण, भक्तिभावाने भरलेला. गणरायाच्या विसर्जनाच्या वेळी गायले जाणारे हे खास भक्तिगीत तुमच्या मनाला स्पर्शून जाईल. 🌸

Credits:-
Singer - Sharmistha bhatkar
Composer - Siddhant Karawde
Lyrics - Traditional

Aarti Lyrics :-
जाहले भजन आम्ही नमितो तव चरण ।
वारुनिया विघ्ने देवा रक्षावे दीना ॥धृ॥

दास तुझे आम्ही देवा तुजलाची ध्यातो
प्रेमे करुनिया देवा गुण तुझेची गातो ॥१॥

तरी द्यावी सिद्धी देवा हेची वासना, देवा हेची वासना
रक्षुनियां सर्वां द्यावी आम्हासी आज्ञा ॥२॥

मागणे ते देवा एकची आहे आता एकची आहे
तारुनियां सकळां आम्हां कृपादृष्टी पाहे ॥३॥

जेव्हां सर्व आम्ही मिळूं ऐशा या ठाया ऐशा या ठाया
प्रेमानंदे लागू तुझी कीर्ति गावया ॥४॥

सदा ऐशी भक्ति राहो आमुच्या मनी देवा आमुच्या मनी
हेची देवा तुम्हा असे नित्य विनवणी ॥५॥

वारुनिया संकटॆ आता आमुची सारी आता आमुची सारी
कृपेची सा‌ऊली देवा दीनावरि करी ॥६॥

निरंतर आमुची चिंता तुम्हां असावी चिंता तुम्हा असावी
आम्हां सर्वांची लज्जा देवा तुम्ही रक्षावी ॥७॥

निरोप घेता आता आम्हा आज्ञा असावी देवा आज्ञा असावी
चुकले आमचे काही त्याची क्षमा असावी ॥८॥

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Now streaming on all audio platforms
♪ Nirop Gheto Ata Amha Adnya Asavi ♪
♪Jio Saavn - https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/nirop-gheto-ata-amha-adnya-asavi/OVsed01Ecmw
♪ Gaana - https://gaana.com/song/nirop-gheto-ata-amha-adnya-asavi

snippet.title: Bijuria | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari | Varun, Janhvi,Sanya, Rohit | Sonu, Tanishk, Ravi, Asees
snippet.description:
Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe giraye re bijuria, bijuria ⚡

A firecracker of a song 🧨, presenting ‘Bijuria’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’! Featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf and Sanya Malhotra in the video, the song is composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Ravi Pawar. Sung by Sonu Nigam and Asees Kaur and penned by Sonu Nigam and Tanishk Bagchi, hit play, turn it up, and let the beat take over! 🔥🎧

#Bijuria #SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #SonuNigam #TanishkBagchi 

Original music composer: Ravi Pawar 
New version reimagined by : Tanishk Bagchi
Singer: Sonu Nigam
Singer: Asees Kaur
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi
Original Lyrics by: Sonu Nigam & Ajay Jhingran
New Version Additional Lyrics by: Tanishk Bagchi
Tabla & Dholak: Raju Sardar, Sanjiv Sen, Sharafat, Arou
Female Chorus: Shudhi Ramani, Abhiruchi Singh, Megha Bhardwaj, Nikitha Venkatesh
Male Chorus: Vivek Naik, Rahul Chitnis, Sagar Lele, Santosh Bote
Chorus Recorded at: Input One
Recording Engineer: Sameer Dharap (Input One)
Chorus Recorded at: Studio 504
Recording Engineer: Rahul M Sharma (Studio 504)
Mix and Master Engineer: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Special Thanks : Hero
Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Directed by Shashank Khaitan

Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Director Of Choreography: Piyush - Shazia
Song Editor: Rishabh Shetty 
Asst Editor: Hrushi

Tujhe lage na najariya,

Oh tujhe lage na najariya, odh le chunariya

Special Thanks: Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria


Lyrics :- 
Tere dil pe haq mera hai
Tu sanam beshaq mera
Phir lakeerein hon ya na ho
Tu mera hai tu mera hai

Jo tu aag hai
Haan to phir mujhe
Jalne ka shauk hai
Jalne ka shauk hai
Marne se kahin
Jyada haan tujhe
Khone ka khauf hai
Khone ka khauf hai

Tu chahiye mujhe
Chahe kahe ise 
Mera junoon ya phir 
Tu zid meri


Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe likh chuka hoon
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi ki
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai 
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera


Paane ki tujhko
Hasrat liye hi
Raaton ko main
Jagta hoon
Kyu jaane phir bhi
Dushaman teri do
Ankhon ko 
Main lagta hoon
Kahe na chahe tu mujhe
Karunga tujhe ishq main
Mujhe ye parwaah nahi 
Jo bhi ho mera anjaam har haal mein
Tu chahiye mujhe
Jo bhi saza mile 
Parwaah hai phir kise
Anjaam ki 
Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe 
Likh chuka hu
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

snippet.title: गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Marathi Song
snippet.description:
गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Savaniee Originals | Marathi Song | Mangalagaur 

About Video 
------------------------------------
नमस्कार! गणपती बाप्पांच्या आगमनानंतर गौराईचे स्वागत हा आपल्या संस्कृतीतील एक अतिशय भावनिक आणि शुभ प्रसंग असतो. त्या सुंदर क्षणांना समर्पित "गौराई गं आली" हे नवे गाणं, Savaniee Original’s Series कडून आपल्या सेवेत सादर करत आहोत.

Gaurai Ga Ali – A melodious and divine Marathi song dedicated to the arrival of Gaurai during Ganpati festival. This heartfelt track celebrates the emotional joy, devotion, and warmth of this sacred tradition in every Marathi home.

🙏 स्वागत करूया गौराईचे – प्रेमाने, भक्तीने आणि आनंदाने!

About Savaniee Ravindrra
--------------------------------------------
Savaniee Ravindrra is an acclaimed Indian playback singer and the recipient of the 67th National Film Award for Best Female Playback Singer for the film Bardo.

She has lent her voice to songs in multiple Indian languages including Marathi, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, Gujarati, Konkani, and Malayalam.

With over 500 performances across the globe, Savaniee has shared the stage with legends like:
🎤 Pt. Hridaynath Mangeshkar
🎤 Hariharan
🎤 Shaan
🎤 Suresh Wadkar
🎤 Ravindra Jain
🎤 Ajay-Atul and many more.
------------------------------------

Savaniee Ravindrra is an acclaimed Indian playback singer and the recipient of the 67th National Film Award for Best Female Playback Singer for the film Bardo.

She has lent her voice to songs in multiple Indian languages including Marathi, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, Gujarati, Konkani, and Malayalam.

snippet.title: New Ranked Mode in Clash of Clans!
snippet.description:
Multiplayer Attacks will be split into Battles and Ranked Battles with the next Clash of Clans update. Judo Sloth Gaming breaks down the blog post which shared this information. In early October the Update will bring the New Ranked Mode from Town Hall 7 and above. Whilst many expected the ‘Legend Rework’ to be only Legend League, this expands it so much further to ensure a wide range of players can take part in the competitive side of the game. The highest leagues will have Battle Modifiers to make them even more competitive. With Ranked Battles being separate to regular multiplayer battles, you can now farm as much as you want, even in the new Legend League. Clash On!

en.title: New Ranked Mode in Clash of Clans!
en.description:
Multiplayer Attacks will be split into Battles and Ranked Battles with the next Clash of Clans update. Judo Sloth Gaming breaks down the blog post which shared this information. In early October the Update will bring the New Ranked Mode from Town Hall 7 and above. Whilst many expected the ‘Legend Rework’ to be only Legend League, this expands it so much further to ensure a wide range of players can take part in the competitive side of the game. The highest leagues will have Battle Modifiers to make them even more competitive. With Ranked Battles being separate to regular multiplayer battles, you can now farm as much as you want, even in the new Legend League. Clash On!

I Finished Rank 3 Global in Clash of Clans: https://youtu.be/4sorgmj9N9s

Thank you for using Code 'Judo' in Clash of Clans to support me.

snippet.description:
नाव गणाचं गोंदायचं | Nav Ganach Gondaych Sukhan Nandaych | Ganpati Trending Song | Rani Maske | SK


गीत - शाहीर विकास लंबोरे

गायिका - राणी मस्के

संगीत - कुलदीप सचिन

कंपोस - SK Brothers

विषेश सहकार्य - राम पाटिल

Recording Studio - SK Star Recording Studio

Instagram I'd Follow Now 👇

https://www.instagram.com/kuldip_sk?igsh=MXhjZXJwb2xidHlkNw==

https://www.instagram.com/sk_star_music_official?igsh=OHN2b3c0M2lqN3R1


नाव गणाचं गोंदायचं
आणि सुखानं नांदायचं
गावदेवाच्या हुकुमानं
नातं नव्यानं सांधायचं..
भेट दिली ही गावदेवानं 2
तुला पवतं बांधायचं..|| 

सरावन, भारावून, मास येतो आनंदात
जागरात गाव येतं गावदेवा पुजून जातं 

देवळाचं राऊळाचं खांब मानाचं ठरलेलं,
बसून तिथं, बांधतात, असं आपलेपणाचं नातं

सुख रखवाली गाऱ्हाणं गणा चरणी मांडायचं ||

वित वित मोजून इथं, सीमा गावाची आखलेली.
सत्वानं, तत्वानं चतुरसीमेला राखलेली..


कणसास, माणसास, देव देतो सारी बरकत
सुख गोडी, भले थोडी, आहे अवघ्यानी चाखलेली

सनासुदीच्या मुहूर्ताला, गुज गणाला सांगायचं.. ||

अशी रीत, कोकणात, एक बांधून इवलं सूत..
काळजात अंतरात कसं गुंफून ठेवी नातं

एकमेव गावदेव धनी चतुरसीमा मालक
अखुरत एकदंत दुजा विश्वाचा चालक

तुम्हा दोघांविना कुणाशी मी हक्कानं भांडायचं

जागरात गाव येतं गावदेवा पुजून जातं 

देवळाचं राऊळाचं खांब मानाचं ठरलेलं,
बसून तिथं, बांधतात, असं आपलेपणाचं नातं

सुख रखवाली गाऱ्हाणं गणा चरणी मांडायचं ||

वित वित मोजून इथं, सीमा गावाची आखलेली.
सत्वानं, तत्वानं चतुरसीमेला राखलेली..


कणसास, माणसास, देव देतो सारी बरकत
सुख गोडी, भले थोडी, आहे अवघ्यानी चाखलेली

सनासुदीच्या मुहूर्ताला, गुज गणाला सांगायचं.. ||

अशी रीत, कोकणात, एक बांधून इवलं सूत..
काळजात अंतरात कसं गुंफून ठेवी नातं

एकमेव गावदेव धनी चतुरसीमा मालक
अखुरत एकदंत दुजा विश्वाचा चालक

तुम्हा दोघांविना कुणाशी मी हक्कानं भांडायचं

snippet.title: Saagar Jaisi Aankhon Wali (Lyrical Video) | Kishore Kumar | R. D. Burman | Revibe | Hindi Songs
snippet.description:
Saagar Jaisi Aankhon Wali – A poetic and unforgettable love song from the classic film Saagar (1985), sung by the legendary Kishore Kumar and composed by the maestro R.D. Burman. The lyrics, written by Javed Akhtar, beautifully describe the depth and beauty of a woman’s eyes — like the vastness of the sea.

Featuring Rishi Kapoor, Kamal Haasan, and Dimple Kapadia, this romantic melody captures a moment of innocent admiration and heartfelt emotion. With its soulful composition, gentle vocals, and graceful visuals, this song remains one of Bollywood’s most cherished expressions of love.

Credits: 
Singer: Kishore Kumar
Music: R. D. Burman
Lyrics: Javed Akhtar
Movie: Saagar
Starring: Rishi Kapoor, Kamal Haasan, Dimple Kapadia
Director: Ramesh Sippy
Producer: G. P. Sippy
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics:

Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Arre tu kya jaane teri khatir  
  
Kitna hai betaab yeh dil  
  
Tu kya jaane dekh raha hai  
  
Kaise kaise khwaab yeh dil  
  
Dil kehta hai tu hai yahan to  
  
Jata lamha tham jaaye  
  
Waqt ka dariya behte behte  
  
Is manzar mein jam jaaye  
  
Tune deewana dil ko banaya  
  
Is dil pe ilzam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Ho aaj main tujhse door sahi  
  
Aur tu mujhse anjaan sahi  
  
Tera saath nahin paaoon to  
  
Khair tera armaan sahi  
  
Ho yeh armaan hain shor nahi ho  
  
Khamoshi ke mele hon  
  
Is duniya mein koi nahi ho  
  
Hum dono hi akele hon  
  
Tere sapne dekh raha hoon  
  
Aur mera ab kaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya
